milestones.description: This is the lowest match aggregate (320) involving teams South Africa & Sri Lanka in ODIs
South Africa's 125-run win against Sri Lanka is the largest margin of victory in terms of runs in ODIs, beating 64-run win against West Indies
Richardson has broken the record for most dismissals in an innings (4) in ODIs for SA, going past Richardson's 3
